## Introduction


The purpose of this document is to present a comprehensive audit of our infrastructure and architecture as of March 10, 2026. This audit focuses on evaluating simulated API error rates, monitoring system throughput, and proposing backend optimizations or database refactoring. This analysis is critical to ensure our technological frameworks support the Forgotten Formula PMA's mission of providing healing over profit and prioritizing nature over synthetic solutions.


